---
// Editorial hero. Typography-first, spacious, Apple/Vercel-inspired.
---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 pt-24 sm:pt-36">
  <p
    class="mb-6 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[var(--color-muted)]"
  >
    Digital Lab
  </p>

  <h1
    class="text-6xl font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ink)] sm:text-8xl"
  >
    AMESOMES
  </h1>

  <p
    class="mt-8 max-w-2xl font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-[var(--color-ink)] sm:text-4xl"
  >
    A digital lab for curious minds.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)]">
    Writing. Experiments. Conversations.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
    <a
      href="/blog"
      class="rounded-full bg-[var(--color-ink)] px-7 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--color-paper)] transition-opacity hover:opacity-85"
    >
      Explore
    </a>
    <a
      href="/about"
      class="rounded-full border border-[var(--color-line)] px-7 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--color-surface)]"
    >
      About
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
